     Really?
         Hand to God.

21:16.209 --> 21:18.142
         You pick a film
         on your computer.

21:18.144 --> 21:20.811
 Three days later,
 there's a disk in your mailbox.

21:20.813 --> 21:22.980
         You got to stay up
         with technology, Marty.

21:22.982 --> 21:24.582
    Wow. Thanks.

